    Spacing_Mark is the current Unicode long-name for this property value.
    The previous name was wrongly carried from glib.

 src/hb-common.h |    2 +-
 src/hb-icu.cc	 |    2 +-
 2 files changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

